// Gamelan Slendro — Javanese pentatonic
// 5 notes: nem barang gulu dada lima
// Stretched octave (period_ratio ≈ 2.02)

@core
@controls
@alphabet.gamelan_slendro:browser
@mm:60

S -> Patet Balungan End

Patet -> nem barang gulu dada lima (wave:triangle, vel:80)
Balungan -> lima _ dada gulu _ barang nem _
End -> nem _ _ _ _ (vel:60)
